The table in @fig:wrenformer-failures shows 456 + 194 (#percent((456 + 194) / 941, precision: 0)) of the failure cases inside the shaded rectangle in the hull distance parity plot come from just two prototypes in spacegroup 71: `AB2C2-oI10-71-a-f-h` and `ABC2-oI8-71-a-b-f`.
The occurrence of those same prototypes in the MP training set shows little data support for the failing prototypes.
