#figure(
  image("figs/diel/diel-parts-vs-bandgap-mp.svg"),
  caption: [
    *Pareto front split by ionic (left) and electronic (right) dielectric contributions.*
    Ionic permittivity tends to be larger and is more likely to break the $1/x$ relationship with $E_"gap"$, making it the more promising property to optimize for computing device applications.
  ],
